com.android.volley.toolbox

Class ImageLoader.BatchedImageRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.android.volley.toolbox.ImageLoader.BatchedImageRequest
  • Enclosing class:
    ImageLoader

    private class ImageLoader.BatchedImageRequest
extends java.lang.Object
    Wrapper class used to map a Request to the set of active ImageContainer objects that are interested in its results.
